dialogue.name: sayori
dialogue.string: "There was one song in that list that popped out to me."

dialogue.name: sayori
dialogue.string: "The song was both happy and upbeat-"

dialogue.name: sayori
dialogue.string: "...and yet it felt really sad too."

dialogue.name: sayori
dialogue.string: "Stuff that's both sad and happy in that way really speaks to me."
